	  	<h5>Antifinger Laminates</h5>
      <p>So smooth!</p>
  	</div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/inddev/image/upload/v1540882919/imagino-banner.jpg" alt="Second slide">
