<br>
<div class="product-grid">
	<br><h3 align="center">Product Database</h3>
	<div class="grid-subtext text-center justify-content-center">
	<p>Navigate to any product listed below to find detailed information about it. The product information is divided into technical and design sections. Some of the areas covered in these sections include-</p>
	<ul class="grid-subtext-ul">
		<li style="text-align:left">How laminates are made</li>
		<li style="text-align:left">How laminates are installed</li>
		<li style="text-align:left">Technical Specifications, Product Features</li>
		<li style="text-align:left">Certifications and Sustainability</li>
		<li style="text-align:left">Sizes, thickness and grades</li>
	</ul>
	<p>Please note that this information is kept upto date on a best effort basis.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-8 container border border-secondary" padding="50px">
		<h5 align="center">HPL Based Products</h5>
		  <ul class="list-unstyled row">
			<% @products.each do |product| %>
		    	<li class="list-item col-2 border-top border-bottom py-2"><%= link_to product.name, products_show_path %></li>
		    <% end %>
		  </ul>
	</div>
	<br>
	<br>	
	<div class="col-8 container border border-secondary" padding="50px">
		<h4 align="center">Compacts Based Products</h4>
			<% @products.each do |product, i| %>
				<%= product.name %>
		    <% end %>
	</div>
</div>

<%= render 'layouts/footer' %>